modName: Seductress x UNP mashup Bodyslide preset
summary: A bodyslide preset that is a mashup of default UNP at 0 weight and Seductress Body by Noveriaa at 100.
descriptionHtml:
I really likedÂ [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/84200/]Seductress Body by Noveriaa[/url] at 100 weight, but, unfortunately,
like with all thick presets out there, its 0 weight wasn't nearly as petite as I would like it (and the breasts looked bad)
That's why I threw this one together. This is pretty much UNP 0 weight at 0 weight and SB 100 weight at 100.
Enjoy!

Be sure to credit the original creator if you want to do anything special with this preset for some reason.
